Introduction

Lee Yebin, known under her stage name May, is a South Korean singer and dancer under THE MUZE Entertainment. She is best known as the main dancer and sub vocalist of the girl group RESCENE.

She was offered a spot in Modhaus's girl group TripleS before debuting as a member of RESCENE on March 26, 2024, with their single album "Re:Scene".
